<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p><a title="Companies > Capcom [2,662 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/capcom">Capcom</a> has released a new trailer for hacking <a title="Genres > Adventure [2,912 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/adventure">adventure game</a> <em><a title="Games > PRAGMATA [13 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/pragmata">PRAGMATA</a></em>, in which protagonists Hugh and Diana meet Eight, a Pragmata just like Diana. <span id="more-1040582"></span></p><p><em>PRAGMATA</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3357650/PRAGMATA/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> on April 17 worldwide. The Switch 2 version is due out on April 24 in Japan.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>Eight Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="PRAGMATA - Eight Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/puTeM4oapmg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
